# Quick Reference - Roadmap Visualization Project

## Project Type
Next.js 15 (App Router) + Supabase + shadcn/ui Roadmap Visualization

## Key Files
- `src/app/page.tsx` - Main roadmap component (client-side)
- `src/lib/db/queries.ts` - Database query functions
- `src/types/database.ts` - TypeScript types
- `supabase/migrations/` - Database migrations

## Quick Commands

### Development
```bash
npm run dev          # Start dev server
npm run build        # Build for production
npm run lint         # Run linter
```

### Database (Supabase CLI)
```bash
supabase db push     # Push migrations
supabase db reset    # Reset database (⚠️ destructive)
```

## Important Rules
1. ✅ ALWAYS use query functions from `src/lib/db/queries.ts`
2. ✅ ALWAYS transform database data with `transformProject()`
3. ✅ NEVER modify shadcn-io components directly
4. ✅ ALWAYS handle async errors gracefully
5. ✅ NEVER commit `.env.local`

